{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"49632e9d31","title":"向“四八”被难烈士致哀","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e15e24b18d","index":0,"year":1946,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"49632e9d31"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"8e7fde1f98","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":11,"text":"一九四六年四月八日，中共政协代表王若飞、政协宪草审议委员会代表秦邦宪、获释不久的前新四军军长叶挺、中共中央职工运动委员会书记邓发等乘美国飞机从重庆回延安，因遇恶劣天气，飞机在山西兴县黑茶山失事，机上人员全部遇难。本篇是毛泽东为烈士们写的祭文。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e4791e484c","type":"title","text":"向“四八”被难烈士致哀","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"8e7fde1f98","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的战友们，不朽的英雄们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"f55739b679","type":"paragraph","text":"数十年间，你们为人民事业做了轰轰烈烈的工作。今天，你们为人民事业而死，虽死犹荣！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"b8286cd25c","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的死是一个号召，它将加深中国人民对于中国共产党的认识，它将加强中国人民坚持和平、民主、团结事业的决心！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"02f4d0cda5","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的死是一个号召，它号召全党党员和全国人民团结起来，为和平、民主、团结的新中国而奋斗到底！","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"39f55f7ae3","type":"paragraph","text":"全党党员和全国人民将继承你们的遗志，继续奋斗，直到胜利，决不懈怠，决不退缩！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"15c376d66b","type":"paragraph","text":"根据一九四六年四月二十日","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"},{"id":"b25caa5147","type":"paragraph","text":"《解放日报》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31"}],"page":{"id":"1c020c4743","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"49632e9d31","start":126,"end":126}}}},"__N_SSG":true}